1221
01:15:04,566 --> 01:15:06,227
Girls, look who's coming.

1222
01:15:09,071 --> 01:15:10,698
How do you do, Pedrito?

1223
01:15:11,106 --> 01:15:12,471
How do you do, baby.

1224
01:15:12,674 --> 01:15:14,642
Is your wife fine?

1225
01:15:14,810 --> 01:15:16,471
She's fine, thanks.

1226
01:15:16,845 --> 01:15:19,439
And what about your
friend Jorge Bueno?

1227
01:15:20,916 --> 01:15:22,042
Is he good?

1228
01:15:24,553 --> 01:15:25,553
Well.

1229
01:15:33,128 --> 01:15:34,128
Pedro!

1230
01:15:34,730 --> 01:15:36,425
What's up General? What
are you doing here?

1231
01:15:36,498 --> 01:15:38,591
- Waiting for you.
- Here I am, please come in.

1232
01:15:39,434 --> 01:15:44,371
No, I'd rather stay here. It's
a very delicate matter.

1233
01:15:45,207 --> 01:15:48,768
You know that Jorge is
engaged to my daughter.

1234
01:15:48,877 --> 01:15:49,605
Yes sir.

1235
01:15:49,711 --> 01:15:52,043
You know that I made public
the engagement.

1236
01:15:52,147 --> 01:15:52,772
Yes sir.

1237
01:15:52,881 --> 01:15:55,645
And you know the banns
are being published.

1238
01:15:55,751 --> 01:15:56,547
Yes sir.

1239
01:15:56,618 --> 01:15:58,245
But what you don't know,

1240
01:15:58,353 --> 01:16:01,550
because in these matters the husband
is the last to know...

1241
01:16:01,723 --> 01:16:04,191
is that your great friend
Jorge Bueno...

1242
01:16:04,393 --> 01:16:06,020
has dishonoured you...

1243
01:16:06,128 --> 01:16:08,619
- Hey General.
- That's the word, sir!

1244
01:16:08,697 --> 01:16:12,724
Dishonoured!, because there's no
other way to name the fact...

1245
01:16:12,801 --> 01:16:15,201
that he sang a serenade
to your wife!

1246
01:16:15,771 --> 01:16:18,672
Shit! That was
really wrong!

1247
01:16:18,740 --> 01:16:20,708
Very bad done, General.

1248
01:16:21,376 --> 01:16:24,470
But since they were friend, maybe
it was just for friendship.

1249
01:16:24,546 --> 01:16:26,844
What friendship, like
hell you will!

1250
01:16:26,949 --> 01:16:28,974
He shouted at her
like a mad man...

1251
01:16:29,084 --> 01:16:32,417
I love you, I love you. Everyone
in the neighbourhood heard him.

1252
01:16:32,654 --> 01:16:33,654
What a shame!

1253
01:16:34,089 --> 01:16:36,284
Imagine my daughter's state.

1254
01:16:36,925 --> 01:16:40,383
To have such an offense on
the verge of the wedding!

1255
01:16:40,696 --> 01:16:42,994
She's been humiliated,
deceived and vilified.

1256
01:16:43,065 --> 01:16:45,033
It's like being kicked
in the teeth!

1257
01:16:46,034 --> 01:16:47,365
Well, general..

1258
01:16:48,170 --> 01:16:51,503
You know a man like me has
no other way but the arms.

1259
01:16:51,740 --> 01:16:55,232
I picked up my gun and I was ready
to wash the infamy with blood.

1260
01:16:55,844 --> 01:16:58,142
But thinking about it carefully,
I concluded...

1261
01:16:58,547 --> 01:17:00,412
That I shouldn't shoot Jorge.

1262
01:17:01,450 --> 01:17:04,010
That's a wise decision, General.
It doesn't worth it.

1263
01:17:04,086 --> 01:17:06,077
I'm not going to shoot him.

1264
01:17:06,288 --> 01:17:07,550
You will!

1265
01:17:07,623 --> 01:17:09,557
- Me?
- Of course!

1266
01:17:09,625 --> 01:17:11,593
Even though I'm deeply
offended...

1267
01:17:11,760 --> 01:17:15,958
I admit the sacred right to punish
that miserable belongs to you...

1268
01:17:16,331 --> 01:17:18,856
- You're right, I'm going to kill him!
- Right!

1269
01:17:18,934 --> 01:17:21,266
He's going to have
the worst death.

1270
01:17:21,536 --> 01:17:23,367
- Civil death.
- What?

1271
01:17:24,172 --> 01:17:27,938
In these matters oblivion is the best
thing, General. Please excuse me.

1272
01:17:28,010 --> 01:17:30,478
No sir! That's no
men's attitude.

1273
01:17:30,545 --> 01:17:32,513
- No?
- It's of cowards.

1274
01:17:32,748 --> 01:17:34,739
- Yes.
- And you're not a coward.

1275
01:17:35,217 --> 01:17:36,878
- No.
- Then, kill him!

1276
01:17:37,386 --> 01:17:40,082
That's the only honourable
way left!

1277
01:17:40,722 --> 01:17:41,722
Yes sir.

1278
01:17:41,790 --> 01:17:43,485
It's the only one.

1279
01:17:43,725 --> 01:17:45,920
Jorge surely dies!

1280
01:17:46,328 --> 01:17:48,193
- See you later, General.
- Where do you think you're going?

1281
01:17:48,296 --> 01:17:49,661
I'm going to take a shower.

1282
01:17:49,731 --> 01:17:53,167
No my friend, you must clean
your honour first...

1283
01:17:53,235 --> 01:17:56,534
and then you take whatever
you want. Let's go

1284
01:18:07,516 --> 01:18:08,516
Genoveva,

1285
01:18:08,550 --> 01:18:12,987
I think you know about that serenade
everybody's talking in town...

1286
01:18:13,088 --> 01:18:16,649
and I must explain my
behaviour telling you frankly

1287
01:18:16,758 --> 01:18:19,921
that when I asked for your hand I
sincerly believed that I was cured...

1288
01:18:20,028 --> 01:18:22,588
from an illness that
deeply affected me...

1289
01:18:22,664 --> 01:18:26,964
Unfortunately that illness has
struck me again so seriously...

1290
01:18:27,069 --> 01:18:32,200
that I think it has no cure.
I think you know it's name.

1291
01:18:32,307 --> 01:18:35,640
I don't want to offend
you repeating it.

1292
01:18:37,679 --> 01:18:40,443
General, would you excuse me?
I'll be back in a moment.

1293
01:18:40,549 --> 01:18:42,574
- Where are you going?
- I'm going er...

1294
01:18:42,684 --> 01:18:45,016
- To pick up my gun.
- There's no need.

1295
01:18:45,120 --> 01:18:47,452
Here's mine.
Take it.

1296
01:18:47,556 --> 01:18:49,080
- I can't accept!
- Why?

1297
01:18:49,157 --> 01:18:50,818
- I implicate you.
- It's best.

1298
01:18:50,892 --> 01:18:53,417
It's going to be a
joint revenge...

1299
01:18:53,495 --> 01:18:57,397
You'll pull the trigger and my
bullets will kill him. Take it!

1300
01:18:58,033 --> 01:19:00,593
Well, we'll take joint revenge.

1301
01:19:02,871 --> 01:19:06,466
By the way, do you want some
soda, General, I'm thristy.

1302
01:19:06,575 --> 01:19:09,908
I'm also thisty, but
of revenge. Let's go!

1303
01:19:10,112 --> 01:19:14,446
I'm not worried because I think your
father will understand and even say.

1304
01:19:15,350 --> 01:19:18,877
Don't worry, Jorgito,
it happens to all men.

1305
01:19:18,987 --> 01:19:24,050
He'll hold my hand as usual,
and he'll invite me to drink.

1306
01:19:24,893 --> 01:19:26,918
Yes sir, Jorge is at
the Post Office.

1307
01:19:27,028 --> 01:19:30,623
- Hurry up!
- General, shouldn't we think it twice?

1308
01:19:30,732 --> 01:19:33,860
It's been analized and solved,
the offender will die!

1309
01:19:33,969 --> 01:19:36,437
Well, and if there
is another guilty?

1310
01:19:36,538 --> 01:19:39,405
How can it be? Do you have
doubts about your wife?

1311
01:19:39,508 --> 01:19:41,601
- Oh no, not at all.
- Then?

1312
01:19:41,943 --> 01:19:45,936
Maybe I was wrong. Jorge
did it with my approval.

1313
01:19:46,014 --> 01:19:48,608
- No.
- Yes.

1314
01:19:48,717 --> 01:19:52,312
Then, the first who's gonna die
it's you, for being yielded!

1315
01:19:52,387 --> 01:19:55,254
- Give me my gun back.
- Please wait, General. Let me explain.

1316
01:19:55,357 --> 01:19:58,622
- There was a reason.
- I'm waiting to hear.

1317
01:19:58,727 --> 01:20:00,991
- Why do I tell you, you won't beleive.
- Come on!

1318
01:20:01,096 --> 01:20:04,361
- It was to save Genoveva.
- My daughter?

1319
01:20:04,466 --> 01:20:06,525
- From what?
- Of getting married to Jorge.

1320
01:20:06,635 --> 01:20:10,002
- It's not for her.
- And what is your business here?

1321
01:20:10,105 --> 01:20:12,869
Because my affection is great,
for her and for you...

1322
01:20:12,974 --> 01:20:15,033
and I had to prevent her
to marry Jorge somehow.

1323
01:20:15,143 --> 01:20:18,374
- But why?
- Because he's...

1324
01:20:18,480 --> 01:20:22,075
- got some kind of illness.
- And illness can be cured. Let's go!

1325
01:20:22,150 --> 01:20:23,981
- Not this one!
- How can you know!

1326
01:20:24,085 --> 01:20:26,883
Science's advanced, and there
are medicines for everything.

1327
01:20:26,955 --> 01:20:30,118
This one can't be cured.
You've got to beleive me.

1328
01:20:30,192 --> 01:20:33,650
Well, if it is a leprosy,
or something like that.

1329
01:20:33,728 --> 01:20:36,959
You've got it! It's not leprosy,
but someting as bad.

1330
01:20:41,670 --> 01:20:43,228
- No...
- Yes.

1331
01:20:43,471 --> 01:20:46,668
Imagine the disgrace for your
daughter and for you.

1332
01:20:46,775 --> 01:20:49,744
Having grandchildren ill-
fated, hunchback..

1333
01:20:49,811 --> 01:20:52,678
Without eyes, or a head this size.

1334
01:20:52,747 --> 01:20:55,079
No, what an atrocity.

1335
01:20:55,283 --> 01:20:59,185
Who would have thought that
on a healthy looking guy.

1336
01:20:59,287 --> 01:21:02,848
It's what he inherited from
his carousing father.

1337
01:21:02,924 --> 01:21:05,415
Well, and what does it have
to do with the serenade?

1338
01:21:05,493 --> 01:21:09,429
Everything! Jorge had kept the secret
and thought to be cured...

1339
01:21:09,531 --> 01:21:13,160
but after the engagement to Genoveva,
he realized that he was ill again...

1340
01:21:13,235 --> 01:21:15,635
and what to do? To tell
you about it? Never!

1341
01:21:15,704 --> 01:21:17,638
You should talk about these things
only to a physician...

1342
01:21:17,706 --> 01:21:22,040
then what to do? To imagine an
affair to dissapoint Genoveva.

1343
01:21:22,143 --> 01:21:24,839
What woman would do
the favor, General?

1344
01:21:24,913 --> 01:21:28,940
Only a friend. We talked to my wife
and Jorge sang the serenade...

1345
01:21:29,050 --> 01:21:30,813
and you know the rest
of the story...

1346
01:21:30,919 --> 01:21:36,152
I see. It was strange taht you
defend the lover of your wife.

1347
01:21:36,224 --> 01:21:38,215
- Of course.
- Yeah, everything is clear now.

1348
01:21:38,326 --> 01:21:40,521
But not the disease.
I don't beleive it!

1349
01:21:40,595 --> 01:21:42,995
- Hey General.
- Let's talk to Jorge!

1350
01:21:43,064 --> 01:21:45,726
- Why do we need to embarrass him?
- Let him get embarrassed!

1351
01:21:45,834 --> 01:21:47,825
I have to clear up this matter.

1352
01:21:47,903 --> 01:21:50,701
And if it is not true this story
about the incurable disease...

1353
01:21:50,772 --> 01:21:53,832
I swear on my father's ashes
an my militar honour

1354
01:21:53,942 --> 01:21:56,137
that I'll shoot you like
a dog. Let's go!

1355
01:22:00,181 --> 01:22:01,181
Jorge!

1356
01:22:04,052 --> 01:22:06,247
I'm here to speak as men do.

1357
01:22:07,289 --> 01:22:09,951
Here I am, General.
What's all about?

1358
01:22:10,125 --> 01:22:12,184
It's about an illness that...

1359
01:22:12,294 --> 01:22:14,091
Well, we have to be clear.

1360
01:22:14,195 --> 01:22:17,255
- Of that disease that you have!
- My disease?

1361
01:22:17,332 --> 01:22:19,562
At least that's what
your friend said.

1362
01:22:19,968 --> 01:22:21,833
And why are you talking
about what you shouldn't?

1363
01:22:21,903 --> 01:22:23,029
I demanded it.

1364
01:22:25,173 --> 01:22:29,303
Well General, in the end I had
to talk about it with you.

1365
01:22:29,411 --> 01:22:33,404
There is the first contradiction. You
said he wouldn't talk to me about it.

1366
01:22:33,515 --> 01:22:35,346
Well, he's changed his mind.

1367
01:22:35,684 --> 01:22:38,175
Well, besides you would
have known by this.

1368
01:22:38,286 --> 01:22:40,948
Letter to Genoveva where
I explain everything.

1369
01:22:41,022 --> 01:22:43,718
- May I read it?
- Yes, why not?

1370
01:22:43,825 --> 01:22:47,522
Hey General, I think it's no good
to learn what friends write.

1371
01:22:47,629 --> 01:22:48,960
Silence!

1372
01:22:53,335 --> 01:22:58,432
I think you know about that serenade
everybody's talking in town

1373
01:22:58,506 --> 01:23:00,474
and I must explain...

1374
01:23:00,942 --> 01:23:05,504
When I asked for your hand I sincerly
thought I was cured from a disease...

1375
01:23:05,613 --> 01:23:07,843
that depply affected me.

1376
01:23:11,786 --> 01:23:15,654
Unfortunately that illness has
struck me again so seriously...

1377
01:23:15,757 --> 01:23:22,060
that I think it has no cure.
I think you know it's name.

1378
01:23:22,163 --> 01:23:24,529
I don't want to offend
you by repeating it.

1379
01:23:24,632 --> 01:23:27,226
No, my daughter musn't
know this.

1380
01:23:27,302 --> 01:23:30,931
She had to know someday.
Maybe she knows it.

1381
01:23:31,039 --> 01:23:33,906
You're so cool about this
embarrassing matter!

1382
01:23:34,009 --> 01:23:36,529
But this is something that happens
to everybody sonner or later.

1383
01:23:36,678 --> 01:23:39,943
General, haven't you been
in such situation?

1384
01:23:40,048 --> 01:23:42,243
Heaven forbid! I'd
rather shot myself!

1385
01:23:42,317 --> 01:23:44,877
General, that's what one says...

1386
01:23:44,953 --> 01:23:47,888
but in the end there's
no shooting, and

1387
01:23:47,989 --> 01:23:51,447
you stay there. It's true
that it makes suffer.

1388
01:23:51,526 --> 01:23:54,723
But when it works, you enjoy it!

1389
01:23:54,796 --> 01:24:00,359
- So you like your disease.
- Yes sir, a lot!

1390
01:24:01,870 --> 01:24:04,361
There is no accountog
for tastes, general.

1391
01:24:04,439 --> 01:24:06,600
You shouldn't speak,
your're like me.

1392
01:24:07,509 --> 01:24:11,445
- You too?
- But I'm not as sick as him.

1393
01:24:12,414 --> 01:24:14,439
God, the world is upside down.

1394
01:24:14,649 --> 01:24:17,209
Do you have a good physician?

1395
01:24:17,318 --> 01:24:20,344
A physician?
No, General.

1396
01:24:20,488 --> 01:24:22,353
These things are not for doctors.

1397
01:24:22,424 --> 01:24:25,154
Either they go by themselves
or they distroy you.

1398
01:24:25,260 --> 01:24:28,286
I don't understand how
can you be resigned.

1399
01:24:28,363 --> 01:24:32,231
How can't it be. Since I was
a kid I have it in my heart.

1400
01:24:32,333 --> 01:24:33,800
You mean in your blood.

1401
01:24:33,868 --> 01:24:37,804
In my heart, blood, soul,
even in my bone marrow.

1402
01:24:37,906 --> 01:24:41,239
You're right. He's
in the final stage.

1403
01:24:41,810 --> 01:24:45,041
But if in spite of all this you
demand that I keep my word...

1404
01:24:45,146 --> 01:24:46,636
I marry your daughter.

1405
01:24:46,714 --> 01:24:51,617
No, no, no. There's no need to
disgrace innocent people...

1406
01:24:51,719 --> 01:24:56,486
ill-fated, hunchback, without
eyes and bigheaded kids.

1407
01:24:56,724 --> 01:24:59,386
Give me your word that you will
never think about my daughter.

1408
01:25:00,295 --> 01:25:02,661
Well, I promise, General.

1409
01:25:03,198 --> 01:25:06,531
Keep up with your plan with Rosario.
I'll make sure that Genoveva will see it.

1410
01:25:06,634 --> 01:25:10,502
I'll take her to your party. There
you can be a little shameless

1411
01:25:10,572 --> 01:25:13,234
so she'll be disappointed, and
I'll have no hard feelings,

1412
01:25:13,308 --> 01:25:17,506
On the contrary, I'll
be very grateful.

1413
01:25:21,015 --> 01:25:23,449
Hey! Why didn't he
shake my hand?

1414
01:25:23,551 --> 01:25:26,349
- Don't push it, buddy don't push it!
- You've got to explain everything!

1415
01:25:26,421 --> 01:25:29,515
Hey man, please, I'll
explain everything.

1416
01:25:31,559 --> 01:25:34,790
Then what, please say
yes, Chayito, please.

1417
01:25:34,896 --> 01:25:37,763
It's clear, Jorge handles
you like a puppet.

1418
01:25:37,832 --> 01:25:43,566
It's like you had a ring in the nose,
and pulls as you pull a, a...

1419
01:25:44,105 --> 01:25:46,369
- A bull?
- Or an ox, it's the same.

1420
01:25:46,441 --> 01:25:49,774
- Chill out, don't be so evil minded.
- You innocent!

1421
01:25:49,844 --> 01:25:53,940
He wants you have another woman, so
I could cheat you with him. He said so!

1422
01:25:54,015 --> 01:25:58,008
And listen, I could cheat you with
every man, but never with Jorge!

1423
01:25:58,119 --> 01:25:59,177
Every man?

1424
01:25:59,888 --> 01:26:02,379
Wll, I meant no-one, and
even less with Jorge

1425
01:26:02,490 --> 01:26:06,551
I only want to make peace, so we
can be friends as we used to...

1426
01:26:06,628 --> 01:26:10,496
- Yes...
- Come on Chayito, please me.

1427
01:26:10,899 --> 01:26:11,899
No!

1428
01:26:18,740 --> 01:26:23,200
Well alright, I'll go to his
party, but I don't want to.

1429
01:26:31,019 --> 01:26:32,145
Shit!

1430
01:26:33,688 --> 01:26:35,713
Hurry up, you're going
to be late to the party.

1431
01:26:35,790 --> 01:26:38,088
Wait, I've got to lock the car.

1432
01:26:38,159 --> 01:26:41,151
Because everyone is honest,
but you never know.

1433
01:26:41,262 --> 01:26:46,825
Hey girl, here comes Mrs. mmm,
mmm's wife and his father.

1434
01:26:46,935 --> 01:26:49,199
Who are mmm and mmmm?

1435
01:26:49,304 --> 01:26:53,070
Those who can't be named
in this house.

1436
01:26:57,011 --> 01:26:58,638
Mmmm.

1437
01:26:58,713 --> 01:27:01,546
Rosario and Pedro are here,
what are we going to do?

1438
01:27:01,616 --> 01:27:03,675
To serve them.
I invited them.

1439
01:27:03,818 --> 01:27:04,818
Jorge!

1440
01:27:07,222 --> 01:27:10,885
They say they're going
to close my paths...

1441
01:27:10,992 --> 01:27:12,857
They could close the paths.

1442
01:27:12,961 --> 01:27:15,953
But my love.
..when?

1443
01:27:16,030 --> 01:27:18,328
- What's up Jorge.
- What's up buddy.

1444
01:27:18,967 --> 01:27:20,958
- Congratulations buddy.
- Thanks buddy.

1445
01:27:21,069 --> 01:27:22,969
Hey buddy, it was very
hard to convince her

1446
01:27:23,037 --> 01:27:25,062
but there she is. Don't
exceed yourself.

1447
01:27:25,139 --> 01:27:27,471
- No, buddy, me?
- What did you tell Maria about me?

1448
01:27:27,542 --> 01:27:30,534
Nothing came to my mind. Let's
see how you can fix it.

